        <updateDate>2020-10-13T14:19:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Personal Needs Allowance Modernization Act or the PNA Modernization Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases the minimum monthly personal needs allowance under Medicaid for an institutionalized individual and couple from $30 to $60 and from $60 to $120, respectively. (The personal needs allowance is deducted from an individual's total income when determining the individual's contribution to the cost of institutionalized care under Medicaid.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
